            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿عَبَسَ﴾: ظَهَرَ التّغَيُّر والعُبُوسُ في وَجْهِ الرَّسُولِ ﷺ.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ﴾: وَأَعْرَضَ.</h2>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "80:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ﴾: لِأَجْلِ أَن جَاءَهُ.</h2>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "80:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ﴾: وأيُّ شَيءٍ يَجْعَلُكَ عالماً بِحَقِيقَةِ أَمْرِهِ؟</p>\n<h2>﴿يَزَّكَّىٰٓ﴾: تَزْكُو نَفسُهُ وَتَطْهُرُ.</h2>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "80:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ﴾: أو يتَّعِظُ.</h2>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "80:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ﴾: عَنْ هَدْيِكَ.</h2>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "80:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَصَدَّىٰ﴾: تَتَعَرَّضُ لَهُ وَتُصْغِي لِكَلامِهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "80:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ﴾: وأيُّ شَيءٍ عَلَيكَ ألَّا يَتَطَهَّرَ مِن كُفْرِهِ؟</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "80:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ﴾: مَن كانَ حَرِيصاً عَلى لِقائِكَ.</h2>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "80:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَخۡشَىٰ﴾: يَخْشَى اللهَ.</h2>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "80:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَلَهَّىٰ﴾: تَتَشاغَلُ.</h2>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "80:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كَلَّآ﴾: ليسَ الأمرُ كما فَعَلْتَ أيُّها الرَّسُولُ.</h2>\n<p>﴿إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ﴾: إنَّ هَذهِ السُّورَةَ مَوعِظَةٌ لَكَ وَلِكُلِّ مَن شَاءَ الاتِّعاظَ.</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "80:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ﴾: فَمَن شَاءَ ذَكَرَ الله وَعَمِلَ بِهَدْيِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "80:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ﴾: هَذا القرآنُ في صُحُفٍ مُعَظَّمَةٍ.</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "80:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مَرۡفُوعَةٖ﴾: عالية القَدْرِ.</h2>\n<p>﴿مُطَهَّرَةِۭ﴾: مُطَهَّرةٍ منَ الدنَسِ والزِّيادةِ والنَّقْصِ.</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "80:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ﴾: بِأيدِي مَلائِكَةٍ يُسْفِرُونَ بالوَحْيِ، أي: يَسْعَونَ بِهِ بَينَ اللهِ ورُسُلِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "80:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كِرَامِۭ﴾: أي عَلى رَبِّهِم.</h2>\n<h2>﴿بَرَرَةٖ﴾: أَخلاقُهُم وأَفعالُهم بارَّةٌ طاهِرَةٌ.</h2>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "80:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ﴾: لُعِنَ الإنسانُ الكَافرُ وعُذِّبَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ﴾: ما أَشَدَّ كُفْرَهُ بِرَبِّهِ!!</h2>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "80:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ﴾: أي: أَوَّلَ مَرَّةٍ؟</h2>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "80:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ﴾: خَلَقَه اللهُ مِن مَّاءٍ قَلِيلٍ، وهو المَنِيُّ.</p>\n<h2>﴿فَقَدَّرَهُۥ﴾: فَقَدَّرهُ أَطْواراً.</h2>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "80:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ﴾: ثم بَيَّنَ لَهُ طَرِيقَ الخيرِ والشَّرِّ.</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "80:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ﴾: فَجَعَلَ لَهُ مَكانًا يُقْبَرُ فِيهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "80:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿أَنشَرَهُۥ﴾: أَحْياهُ، وَبَعَثَهُ بَعْدَ مَوتِهِ للْحِسابِ والجَزاءِ.</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "80:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿كَلَّا﴾: ليسَ الأمرُ كما يقُولُ الكَافِرُ وَيَفْعَلُ.</h2>\n<p>﴿لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ﴾: لم يُؤَدِّ ما أَمَرهُ اللهُ بِهِ.</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "80:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ﴾: فَلْيَتَدَبَّرِ الإنْسانُ: كَيفَ خَلَقَ اللهُ طَعامَه الَّذِي هُوَ قِوَامُ حياتِهِ؟</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "80:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ﴾: أَنْزَلَنَاهُ.</h2>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "80:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ﴾: أي: بِما أَخْرَجْنا مِنْها مِن نَّباتٍ شَتَّى.</p>"
        },
        "27": {
